data.description: Experience luxury living at its finest in this expansive penthouse duplex located in the heart of Buena Park. Boasting 2200 square feet of sun-drenched space, this residence offers unparalleled comfort and style with lake views and an abundance of premium features.Upon entering, you are greeted by an inviting open floor plan accentuated by two fireplaces, hardwood floors, and skylights that flood the space with natural light. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring stainless steel appliances and granite countertops.Adjacent to the kitchen is a spacious dining area ideal for hosting intimate gatherings or festive dinners.This exceptional residence offers three generously sized bedrooms, each with its own full bath, providing ultimate privacy and convenience. The primary suite, a true oasis, boasts a luxurious bathroom, in-unit washer and dryer, and a private entrance for added exclusivity.With four zones of individually controlled heating and cooling, you can customize your comfort throughout the home. Step outside onto the Juliette balconies and  take advantage of the covered parking, private storage room and bike rack for added convenience.Residents of this premier building enjoy access to a small gym on the first floor, perfect for staying active without leaving home. Plus, with the Sheridan L station just a 15-minute walk away and a plethora of amenities nearby including a golf course, tennis courts, biking/hiking trails, and an array of restaurants and grocery stores, everything you need is right at your fingertips.Don't miss this rare opportunity to own the penthouse suite that everyone in the building covets.
